title: Mobile Uncle Tools Package
description:
This is a "package" that i have created that includes the mobile uncle tools for android devices, along with the mobile uncle tools imei writer. These tools can help people who have android devices (samsung devices not supported, for that you need to search for modem firmware specific to your device) that have corrupted IMEI numbers, and thus cannot register the simcards to the network. 

I do not take credit for the software in this package, i am just uploading it, along with a txt file that serves as instructions on how to rewrite your IMEI.

NOTE*** You have to have root access for this to work!

I take no responsibility if you damage your phone, use at own risk! (If you dont know what this is, you shouldnt be downloading it anyway)
